<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>[Your Name] | Student Portfolio</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      background: #f6fbff;
      color: #172033;
      font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .navbar {
      align-items: center;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dbeafe;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      left: 0;
      padding: 18px 7%;
      position: sticky;
      right: 0;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .logo {
      align-items: center;
      color: #075cab;
      display: flex;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .logo-icon {
      align-items: center;
      background: #0b74d1;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #fff;
      display: inline-flex;
      height: 36px;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 36px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 26px;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: #42526b;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #0b74d1;
    }

    .hero {
      align-items: center;
      display: grid;
      gap: 56px;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 74px);
      padding: 72px 7% 84px;
    }

    .badge {
      background: #e6f2ff;
      border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #075cab;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      color: #0f2442;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.7rem);
      letter-spacing: 0;
      line-height: 1.02;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      color: #0b74d1;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: #52627a;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      max-width: 650px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .btn {
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: inline-flex;
      font-weight: 700;
      gap: 10px;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #0b74d1;
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(11, 116, 209, 0.24);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
      color: #075cab;
    }

    .profile-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(16, 76, 128, 0.14);
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .profile-placeholder {
      align-items: center;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11, 116, 209, 0.9), rgba(44, 151, 255, 0.72)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) 0 10px, transparent 10px 20px);
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 280px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .profile-placeholder .avatar-icon {
      font-size: 5rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .profile-placeholder strong {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .quick-info {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .quick-info div {
      align-items: center;
      background: #f1f7ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .quick-info span {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 76px 7%;
    }

    .section-header {
      margin: 0 auto 34px;
      max-width: 720px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      color: #0f2442;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-header p {
      color: #5b6b82;
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 22px;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    }

    .panel,
    .skill-card,
    .contact-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(16, 76, 128, 0.08);
      padding: 26px;
    }

    .panel h3,
    .skill-card h3,
    .contact-card h3 {
      color: #0f2442;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .panel p,
    .skill-card p,
    .contact-card p {
      color: #5b6b82;
    }

    .details-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .details-list li {
      background: #f1f7ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #0b74d1;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    .details-list strong {
      color: #0f2442;
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .skills-grid,
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .icon-box {
      align-items: center;
      background: #e6f2ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #075cab;
      display: flex;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      height: 54px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      width: 54px;
    }

    .contact {
      background: #eaf5ff;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #0f2442;
      color: #dbeafe;
      padding: 26px 7%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero,
      .about-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 52px;
      }

      .skills-grid,
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .navbar {
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .nav-links {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px 18px;
      }

      .hero,
      .section {
        padding-left: 5%;
        padding-right: 5%;
      }

      .hero-actions,
      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .skills-grid,
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a class="logo" href="#home">
      <span class="logo-icon">ICT</span>
      <span>[Your Name]</span>
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div>
        <span class="badge">Future ICT Professional</span>
        <h1>Hello, I am <span>[Your Name]</span>.</h1>
        <p>
          A motivated student from [Your School Name] who enjoys learning technology,
          solving problems, and building a strong foundation for a future career as
          [Your Dream Career].
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Contact Me</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#skills">View Skills</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="profile-card" aria-label="Student profile summary">
        <div class="profile-placeholder">
          <div class="avatar-icon">👤</div>
          <strong>Profile Image</strong>
          <p>Add your photo here</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-info">
          <div><span>🏫</span><p><strong>School:</strong> [Your School Name]</p></div>
          <div><span>💼</span><p><strong>Dream Career:</strong> [Your Dream Career]</p></div>
          <div><span>📘</span><p><strong>Favourite Subject:</strong> [Your Favourite Subject]</p></div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="about">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
          A short introduction to my personality, interests, and goals as a student
          preparing for opportunities in information and communication technology.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <article class="panel">
          <h3>Who I Am</h3>
          <p>
            My name is [Your Name]. I am a student at [Your School Name] with a strong
            interest in ICT, digital tools, and creative problem solving. I enjoy learning
            how technology can improve everyday life and help people work smarter.
          </p>
          <p>
            My dream career is to become [Your Dream Career]. I am building my confidence,
            communication skills, and technical knowledge step by step so I can succeed in
            school and in my future profession.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="panel">
          <h3>Personal Details</h3>
          <ul class="details-list">
            <li><strong>Full Name</strong>[Your Name]</li>
            <li><strong>Hobbies</strong>[Your Hobbies]</li>
            <li><strong>Favourite Subject</strong>[Your Favourite Subject]</li>
            <li><strong>Dream Career</strong>[Your Dream Career]</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="skills">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <p>
          These skills support my journey as a future ICT professional and help me grow
          as a confident, responsible student.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="skills-grid">
        <article class="skill-card">
          <div class="icon-box">💻</div>
          <h3>Computer Literacy</h3>
          <p>Comfortable using digital tools, school platforms, and productivity software.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="skill-card">
          <div class="icon-box">🧠</div>
          <h3>Problem Solving</h3>
          <p>Able to think carefully, ask questions, and find practical solutions.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="skill-card">
          <div class="icon-box">🌐</div>
          <h3>Web Interest</h3>
          <p>Interested in websites, online systems, design, and how the internet works.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="skill-card">
          <div class="icon-box">🤝</div>
          <h3>Teamwork</h3>
          <p>Enjoys working with classmates, sharing ideas, and completing group tasks.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="skill-card">
          <div class="icon-box">🗣️</div>
          <h3>Communication</h3>
          <p>Practices clear speaking, active listening, and respectful discussion.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="skill-card">
          <div class="icon-box">📈</div>
          <h3>Growth Mindset</h3>
          <p>Willing to learn from mistakes and keep improving through practice.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section contact" id="contact">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Get in touch for school projects, ICT activities, teamwork opportunities,
          or student portfolio discussions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-grid">
        <article class="contact-card">
          <div class="icon-box">✉️</div>
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p>your.email@example.com</p>
        </article>
        <article class="contact-card">
          <div class="icon-box">📍</div>
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>[Your City / Area]</p>
        </article>
        <article class="contact-card">
          <div class="icon-box">🎓</div>
          <h3>School</h3>
          <p>[Your School Name]</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>© 2026 [Your Name]. Student Portfolio for a Future ICT Professional.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
